gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 136, 76ers 121
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nets defeated the 76ers, 136-121. Cam Thomas led the way with 40 points, five assists, and three rebounds for the Nets, with Mikal Bridges adding 23 points, four assists, and three rebounds in the victory. Tyrese Maxey tallied 23 points, five assists, and three rebounds for the 76ers in the losing effort. The Nets improve to 20-28, while the 76ers fall to 30-18.
